OL,3,CCould school Lego clubs get more girls
OL,4,Cinto STEM?
OL,6,FA group of Wrexham teenagers hope
OL,7,Ftheir tubs of Lego will land them a
OL,8,Fticket to Texas after building and
OL,9,Fprogramming a robot from scratch.
OL,11,FThe girls from Ysgol Morgan Llwyd have
OL,12,Fgiven up their lunch breaks to learn
OL,13,Fcoding and build 'Jac,' a robot
OL,14,Fentirely made from Lego.
OL,16,FThey will now compete against other
OL,17,Fschools in north Wales in March, with
OL,18,Fa national engineering competition to
OL,19,Ffollow.
