OL,3,CCould school Lego clubs get more girls
OL,4,Cinto STEM?
OL,6,FIf successful, the pupils hope to land
OL,7,Fa spot in a worldwide competition in
OL,8,FTexas.
OL,10,FHead of Design and Technology at the
OL,11,Fschool Jessica Evans says it has been
OL,12,Fa "great experience."
OL,14,FShe told ITV Wales: "Lego club came
OL,15,Fabout last year. The pupils wanted to
OL,16,Ftake part in a robotics competition.
OL,17,F"Prior to that I had no knowledge
OL,18,Fwhatsoever of robotics so I got my
OL,19,Fhead down and learnt to code."
