OL,3,CCould school Lego clubs get more girls
OL,4,Cinto STEM?
OL,6,FThe school was asked to take part by
OL,7,Fthe charity Engineering Education
OL,8,FWales.JThey held the First Lego League
OL,9,FChallenge on behalf of the Institute
OL,10,Fof Engineering Technology.JLast year
OL,11,Fthey won the North Wales heat and went
OL,12,Fthrough to the UK final.
OL,14,FYear 11 pupil Grace has enjoyed
OL,15,Fhelping the younger students with the
OL,16,FLego club.JShe said: "I really like
OL,17,Fhow this year it's a team of all girls.
