OL,3,CCould school Lego clubs get more girls
OL,4,Cinto STEM?
OL,6,F"There's a big demand for women in
OL,7,FScience, Technology, Engineering and
OL,8,FMaths and I think it's important to
OL,9,Fencourage younger pupils to take up
OL,10,FSTEM activities".
OL,12,FIt is hoped the project will make the
OL,13,Fgirls think of a career in what can be
OL,14,Fa male-dominated environment.
