OL,3,CCould school Lego clubs get more girls
OL,4,Cinto STEM?
OL,6,FMs Evans said: "I'm a big believer in
OL,7,Fgetting more girls into STEM subjects,
OL,8,Fit's a brilliant career for them.
OL,9,F"There's a massive deficit in people
OL,10,Fgoing into STEM jobs in the first
OL,11,Fplace and let alone girls so I think
OL,12,Fit's a good place to do this
OL,13,Fcompetition and get a bit of a love
OL,14,Ffor the subject.
OL,16,FAs well as building the robot, they
OL,17,Fhave put together a website and a
OL,18,Fboard which 'Jac' has to move around.
