OL,6,FPupil Sophie said "There are a lot of
OL,7,Fthings the robot has to do. It has to
OL,8,Fpick up things, push things and move
OL,9,Fthings around the board."
OL,11,FFor Lottie, learning coding has been
OL,12,Fabout discovering something she never
OL,13,Fknew she'd enjoy.JShe said: "I never
OL,14,Freally knew how to code, my brother's
OL,15,Freally good at stuff like that but
OL,16,FI've never really been interested in
OL,17,Fit before."
